{"questionId":"9076669","questionHtml":"<p>A beam of monochromatic light is incident on a diffraction grating of <em>N </em>lines per unit length.&nbsp;The angle between the first orders is <em>θ</em><sub>1</sub>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"https://ib-questionbank-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/tinymce_asset/asset/4828/Schermafbeelding_2018-08-13_om_18.48.12.png\" alt=\"M18/4/PHYSI/HPM/ENG/TZ2/26\"></p>\n<p>What is the wavelength of the light?</p>\n<p>A.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{\\sin {\\theta _1}}}{N}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>sin</mi>\n      <mo>⁡</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>θ</mi>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mi>N</mi>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em>N</em> sin&nbsp;<em>θ</em><sub>1</sub></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em>N</em> sin<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\frac{{{\\theta _1}}}{2}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <msub>\n              <mi>θ</mi>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </msub>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </mfrac>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>D.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{\\sin \\left( {\\frac{{{\\theta _1}}}{2}} \\right)}}{N}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>sin</mi>\n      <mo>⁡</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mrow>\n                <msub>\n                  <mi>θ</mi>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                </msub>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mi>N</mi>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"9076669","referenceCode":"18M.1.HL.TZ2.26","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"A beam of monochromatic light is incident on a diffraction grating of N lines per unit length. The angle between the first orders is θ1. What is the wavelength of the light? A. sin","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"26","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Additional higher level (AHL)","Additional higher level (AHL)","Topic 9: Wave phenomena","9.3 – Interference","Additional higher level (AHL)","Topic 9: Wave phenomena"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}